<!--StartFragment-->

David A Etta AKA (David King or David Etta King) is an Award-Winning Gospel music minister, Song-Writer, Producer, and Author whose ministerial impact has affected the lives of many Africans, Europeans, and Americans and the world.

He is the Founder of David Etta Ministry International (DAMI), David King Institute of Music and Sound, and The Fragrance Of Worship (TheFOW).

He was born in South West Region, Buea, Cameroon.

Married to Sonita Mutang

The Artist has released two albums and over five singles.

Albums

1: The voice of Change. 2: Worthy Lamb

Singles:

* Winner for Life
* Stand in Awe
* You Ft Ray Robinson
* No one ft Gabriel Eziashi
* God is Everywhere

He is an author of over five books:

* Dominion Consciousness
* Praise and Worship Manual
* How to Sing Better
* Principle and benefits of service
* Know your ABC as a Christian

David Etta has a heart for God and gospel music. He hosted Frank Edwards in 2019 Live in Dallas, Texas, and has shared the stage with so many great men and women of God.

David Etta's mission is to train and to equip music ministers for effectiveness life and ministry, and also to raise the banner of praise and worship across the Globe.

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RC5VywubwqM
